**Simplest way** (simple collect - supports parallel streams):

    public static &lt;T&gt; Stream&lt;T&gt; reverse(Stream&lt;T&gt; stream) {
        return stream
                .collect(Collector.of(
                        () -&gt; new ArrayDeque&lt;T&gt;(),
